title: Day 1
text:
This is my first blog post! Here are my reflections and notes from day 1.



How to set up a Quarto blog
The importance of YAML frontmatter
How to write content in Markdown




Here’s a simple example:

# A simple Python example
greeting = "Hello, world!"
print(greeting)

# Some basic math
numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
total = sum(numbers)
print(f"The sum is: {total}")

Hello, world!
The sum is: 15





Tomorrow I plan to:

Explore more Quarto features
Add some visualizations
Learn about themes and styling

That’s all for today!
